Symbol.Script_VL:
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Styles ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- values "stStyle" stStyles values "iStyle" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stStyle" then iStyle = 1 if stStyle = stStyles[2] then iStyle = 2 parameters iStyle = iStyle else stStyle = stStyles[1] if iStyle = 2 then stStyle = stStyles[2] parameters stStyle = stStyle endif ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Elev Type ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- values "elevtyp" stElevTypes values "iElevType" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iElevType" then elevtyp = stElevTypes[1] if iElevType = 2 then elevtyp = stElevTypes[2] parameters elevtyp = elevtyp else iElevType = 1 if elevtyp = stElevTypes[2] then iElevType = 2 parameters iElevType = iElevType endif ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Symbol Styles ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- values "styp" stSymbolTypes values "iSymbolType" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iSymbolType" then styp = stSymbolTypes[1] if iSymbolType = 2 then styp = stSymbolTypes[2] parameters styp = styp else iSymbolType = 1 if styp = stSymbolTypes[2] then iSymbolType = 2 parameters iSymbolType = iSymbolType endif ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Shower Tray Type ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- if not(gs_symbol_type_enable) then values "shtyp" stShowerTypes[1], stShowerTypes[2] values "iShowerType" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "shtyp" then iShowerType = 1 if shtyp = stShowerTypes[2] then iShowerType = 2 parameters iShowerType = iShowerType else shtyp = stShowerTypes[1] if iShowerType = 2 then shtyp = stShowerTypes[2] parameters shtyp = shtyp endif else values "shtyp" stShowerTypes values "iShowerType" 1, 2, 3
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "shtyp" then iShowerType = 1 if shtyp = stShowerTypes[2] then iShowerType = 2 if shtyp = stShowerTypes[3] then iShowerType = 3 parameters iShowerType = iShowerType else shtyp = stShowerTypes[1] if iShowerType = 2 then shtyp = stShowerTypes[2] if iShowerType = 3 then shtyp = stShowerTypes[3] parameters shtyp = shtyp endif endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Limitations ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
values "a" range [0.10, ) values "b" range [0.10, )
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "elevtyp" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "iElevType" then a = defaultSizes[iElevType][1] b = defaultSizes[iElevType][2]
parameters a = a, b = b endif
if gs_cont_pen = 0 then Parameters gs_cont_pen = 8 if gs_fill_pen = 0 then Parameters gs_fill_pen = 91
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! UI ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
values "gs_ui_current_page" 1
Symbol.Script_1D:
dim stStyles[2] stStyles[1] = `Простой` stStyles[2] = `Угол`
dim stElevTypes[2] stElevTypes[1] = `Верх` stElevTypes[2] = `Сторона`
dim stSymbolTypes[2] stSymbolTypes[1] = `Простой` stSymbolTypes[2] = `Детальный`
dim stShowerTypes[3] stShowerTypes[1] = `Тип 1` stShowerTypes[2] = `Тип 2` stShowerTypes[3] = `Тип 3`
Symbol.Script_UI:
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
TABID_ROOT = -1 TABID_STYLES = 1
if TABID_STYLES > 0 then ui_page TABID_STYLES, TABID_ROOT, `Стили Душевых Кабин`, "uiTab_Style_flat(1)" gosub "stylesPage" endif
! ============================================================================= end ! =============================================================================
"stylesPage": pageStartY = 5
ui_infield{3} "iStyle", 0, pageStartY, 444, 260, 1, 1, 2, 1, 132, 162, 128, 128, 1, stStyles[1], 1, 2, stStyles[2], 2 return
Symbol.Comment: Различные типы прямоугольного 2D-символа поддона душа, вид сверху или сбоку.
